IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: LIST OF EXHIBITS CyberTip 162252188 CyberTip 162305807 CyberTip 162736146 Google Preservation Letter Endorsed Verizon Subpoena Endorsed T-Mobile Subpoena Endorsed Comcast Subpoena NARRATIVE On 5/23/2023the Maryland State Police Internet Crimes Against Children (ICAC) task force received CyberTip: 162252188 from the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (NCMEC). The CyberTip, which wasreported by Google, was generated by the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (NCMEC) due to Google reporting that on 1/23/2021at 06:21:53UTCsuspectedchild pornography was uploaded from an IP address geo-locating to Hyattsville, MD. It should be noted; the suspected child pornography was uploaded to the Google Photos and Google Drive infrastructure. Google provided the following information: Name: Misa Reyes Mobile Phone: +12407906617 (Verified 05-26-2020 19:33:45 UTC) Mobile Phone: +12404089526 (Verified 05-22-2014 21:05:05 UTC) Date of Birth: 08-28-1986 Email Address: misareyes66@gmail.com (Verified) IP Address: 2607:fb91:14a7:95a4:ee02:b465:9057:3604 (T-Mobile) (Login) on 04-29-2023 at 01:06:08 UTC. Deconfliction:162305807, 162736146 TFC Mueller reviewed the associated CyberTip and observed 13 files of child pornography.List below are descriptions of three files. (Comcast) On 5/30/2023 TFC Mueller authored a preservation letter, for misareyes66@gmail.com, and submitted it to Google. On 5/30/2023 TFC Mueller authored a subpoena for all of the above listed IP addresses, as well as newest login to the suspect account, and submitted the subpoenas to the Howard County States Attorneys Office for endorsement. On 5/30/2023 TFC Mueller observed other related CyberTips to 162252188 and field a request to NCMEC for the other associated CyberTips. On 6/1/2023 TFC Mueller received the endorsed T-Mobile subpoena and submitted it to T-Mobile. On 6/1/2023 TFC Mueller received the endorsed Comcast subpoena and submitted it to Comcast. Case Open, investigation ongoing.
LIST OF EXHIBITS Verizon Subpoena Response NARRATIVE On 6/6/2023 TFC Mueller received the Verizon subpoena response. Verizon does not retain records from 2021. Case Open, investigation ongoing.

LIST OF EXHIBITS T-Mobile Response Comcast Response Cert. NARRATIVE On 6/14/2023 TFC Mueller received the T-Mobile subpoena response. T-Mobile was unable to provide any records, due to the time of the IPV6 being used being outside 90 days. On 6/27/2023 TFC Mueller received the Comcast endorsed response. Comcast was unable to provide any records dude to the amount of past time. Given the occurrence date(s) associated with this CyberTip(s), and numerous subpoenas submitted in an attempt to gain investigative leads which failed, I request this investigation be suspended.
